# {{ .projectName }}

Elasticsearch Logstash and Kibana log aggregation stack.

## Quick Start

    cp .env.example .env
    docker compose up -d

## Access

* Elasticsearch: http://localhost:{{ .esPort }}
* Kibana: http://localhost:{{ .kibanaPort }}
* Logstash Beats input: localhost:{{ .logstashBeatsPort }}
* Logstash TCP input: localhost:{{ .logstashTcpPort }}

Send JSON log lines to the TCP input: echo '{"message": "hello"}' | nc localhost {{ .logstashTcpPort }}
